						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Slab standing near a dharmaśālā.</hi></p>						

						<p>12th-13th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged and worn out record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">12th-13th Century A.D.,</hi> seems to register a gift of land to a deity. It refers to Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara <hi rend="bold">Brahma-bhūpa</hi> who is eulogised at great length.</p>						

						<p>1) The rest is worn out.</p>						

